headline: 3 Healthcare Stocks Walking a Fine Line
summary: From novel pharmaceuticals to telemedicine, most healthcare companies are on a mission to drive better patient outcomes. Shareholders who bet on the industry have been rewarded lately as healthcare stocks have returned 10.8% over the past six months, topping the S&P 500 by 4.1 percentage points.
